Uses of Package
org.activebpel.rt.util

Packages that use org.activebpel.rt.util
org.activebpel.rt.bpel This package contains classes for creating a BPEL model and for implements a standalone BPEL engine for testing designs. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def This package contains base classes and elements used to create BPEL model definitions. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl This package contains the base classes used in the implementation model for the BPEL activities. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.activity.support Includes supporting bpel objects which aren't properly activities.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.attachment   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.reply   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.visitors Classes that visit a tree of BPEL implementation objects and save or restore their state.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server Root package for the Active Endpoints BPEL Engine.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.catalog.resource This package contains the resource catalog, its associated interfaces and helper classes. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine The BPEL engine, support classes, and engine factory.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.process This package contains classes related to process management.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.recovery This package contains classes for recovering or regenerating the state of a process from alarms, messages, or faults that the process received. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.recovery.test This package contains classes for testing the functionality of the recovery engine. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.storage This package contains classes for storing the state of BPEL processes to an external storage facility. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.storage.providers   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.storage.sql This package contains classes for storing the state of BPEL processes to a SQL database. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.storage.xmldb.process Contains the storage classes that implement a XMLDB version of the Process storage.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.storage.xmldb.transreceive   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.logging In-memory and persistent logging facilities.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.transreceive This package contains the transmission tracker and it's related classes.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.urn   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.xpath.ast.visitors   
org.activebpel.rt.util Utility classes for XML handling, reading JARs, I/O, and a blocking queue.  
org.activebpel.work The work manager and friends, which provide a facility for scheduling asynchronous operations.
